Short:        Point'n click adv. `Adventure2 Remake`
Author:       Quantum Code Monk
Uploader:     quantumcodemonk@outlook.com
Type:         game/role
Version:      1.1.1
Architecture: m68k-amigaos
Distribution: Itch.io and Aminet

Description
'Adventure 2 Remake' is a point and click adventure written with Scala MM400. 
The game is a graphic version of the text adventure `Adventure 2`.

Music by MisthaLu, indiegamemusic.com, used with his kind permission. 

Requirements
Requires a copy of Scala or Scala Player to run, not included in this release.
It should run on almost any Amiga with a minimum resolution of 
640*512 (16 colors) running AmigaOS 3.x.
Tested on AmigaOS3.2 and Scala MM300/MM400.

Installation
Unpack the files to any location. 
Add the assign below from cli (or in your startupfile):
Assign: adv2remake: <installation folder>

How to play
Point and click!

